26 May 2012: 1.1.14 Miek Gieben <miek@miek.nl>
   * [rdup] check for the existence of ._rdup_. files and parse its contents
     to restore the actual files' ownership
   * [rdup-up] save user/group info in ._rdup_. files when chown(1)ing them has failed.
     Useful when backing up via sshfs. See rdup(1) section "Non-root backups"
   * [rdup-up] add -u flag to suppress creating these ._rdup_. files. (useful when restoring)
   * [rdup] add -u flag to suppress interpreting these ._rdup_. files.


18 Feb 2012: 1.1.13 Miek Gieben <rdup@miek.nl>
   * Make rdup-tr compile when libnettle was not found (Miek Gieben)
   * Fix for very large inodes and filesizes (Kojedzinszky Richard)
   * Fix tar/pax output when the filesize of files changes (rdup -Pgzip for
     instance) (Reported by: Alejandro Pulver). This created files padded
     with zero bytes.


